d12c9245ce9ab4fc89bf8be908b3","tid":357750,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食肉菌   不了</blockquote><br />\n用食水架"},{"pid":"60e25c24f5e9182cabcb397f267227ae1d71ff4b","tid":357750,"uid":114164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食肉菌   不了</blockquote><br />\n用食水架</blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2260e1880023292954e9db11485aab1e1e5d76","tid":357750,"uid":114164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fcbf3dd98ea52ae258c243d238743575220288","tid":357750,"uid":114164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db5c292f8edb54fce7ead6dfa1e34ec72f72be2","tid":357750,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>裝咗ROCA個隻洗pat pat廁板<br />\n日日都會洗pat pat<br />\n樓主去衛浴產品店睇下啦  旺角/灣仔都有大把<br />\n<br />\n屎塔好似$2000+<br />\n廁板好似$4000+<br />\n但無買錯  買得岩<br />\n<br />\n買張顯示卡  依家都要5000蚊打上啦<br />\n換部濕鳩電話  都要幾千啦<br />\n買個好D既廁所   自己每一日都enjoy到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 儲定錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n畀多D資料你地參考<br />\n我買既係 Roca牌，&quot;The Gap&quot;系列，另加左個廁板用淡水洗pat pat，<br />\n個期全屋裝修所以買<br />\n裝修時同師父講個度要有相關既水供應就得，佢地好熟手，知道係要點做<br />\n<br />\n至於有人話，有時便便個時，屎塔會痴住D屎，<br />\n要用清潔刷刷屎，刷完又放返個刷去個座度<br />\n<br />\n我舊時個屎塔  都係咁  會痴屎 + 要搵野刷<br />\n換左屎塔之後，<br />\n唔知係咪佢設計直上直落<br />\n<strong>完美100%不痴屎</strong>，都唔知係咩科技，定係有塗層<br />\n我上年到依家   應該接近用左12個月了<br />\n日日都有人會便便<br />\n無論我地點樣便便，都唔會痴屎<br />\n一沖 就唔會有屎<br />\n至今全屋都無買刷屎塔既刷   完全不需要"},{"pid":"9aa548a61d1d51984